tags.name: Rang Mahal

tags.description: It is a building that housed the baths and was used by the emperors. In the eastern apartment of Hammam, there is a dressing room. In the western department, hot water flows through the taps. The interiors of Hammam were decorated with white marble.
tags.name: Hammam

tags.description: One of the small palaces in Red Fort built by Bahadur Shah Zafar, the last Mughal emperor. It's in a decaying condition but very clean and still beautiful.
tags.name: Zafar Mahal
